        <Parent_String>metalworking wrenches [300023371], metal-joining and -holding tools [300162883], equipment for metal-joining and -holding [300023311], metalworking equipment [300162819], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
